<!--
In the MetraTech RMP 1.3 to 2.1,
The MOM application come by default with a standard menu.
it is possible to set the MOM Payment server menu (AKA Step-MOM) and for demo purpose it possible to set
all options available menu.

In 2.2 we added some new features called MOM Consoles (Non Documented) Features which are off
by default.

Because we have so much menus, we changed the way to configure the MOM menu.

The file MOM\default\LinkLoopUp\Menus.Definition.xml contains the entry MOM_MENU_DEFINITION which
definitin the menu configuration to use.

The default menu configuration are implemeted in the same file as csv file name list: 
STANDARD_MENU_LIST, PAYMENT_SERVER_MOM_MENU_LIST, ALL_MOM_MENU_LIST.

If you need to customize the menu, you must copy all the files from MOM\default\menu to
MOM\custom\menu and update the XML Entry MOM_MENU_DEFINITION_FOLDER in the same file.
-->